I got this for my 1.5 yr. old andI got this one thinking it was a 5 hour playing time as the product description said. It is actually only 51 min. long, which is 40 minutes LESS than alot of the other dvd's such as the "Friends" Tom and Jerry disk. I was very disappointed in the wrong info on the Amazon website. It costs the same as the Friends one I got at CVS for $5.00 that has way more episodes. The worst part about this DVD is that the actual content and story lines are newer and don't feel like the classic Tom and Jerry of my childhood. There are many violent scenes for young kids which was also a major turn off of this DVD. Only has 6 episodes!! Awful content!!
